glass-card = 'bg-white/70 border border-white/20 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-md'
Responsive grid: grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-...
Animated scroll: Framer Motion initial/animate/whileInView
Lightbox modal for diagrams / video: see LightboxModal, DemoVideoModal components above
*/

